---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services & Pricing | Twisted Oak Taxidermy" description="Taxidermy services and pricing for deer, predators, birds, turkey, and small game mounts. Local taxidermist near Mount Airy, NC.">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal text-center mb-4">
        Services & Pricing
      </h1>
      <p class="text-center text-earth mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Quality craftsmanship at fair prices. All mounts include a custom form fitting and professional finishing.
      </p>

      <!-- Deposit Notice -->
      <div class="bg-tan/10 border border-tan/30 rounded-lg p-4 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-earth-dark font-medium">
          <strong>50% deposit required</strong> at drop-off. Remaining balance due at pickup.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Deer Taxidermy -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 border-b-2 border-tan pb-2">
          Deer Taxidermy
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Shoulder Mount (Standard)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$650</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Standard whitetail shoulder mount. Includes form, eyes, and finishing. Upright, semi-sneak, or full sneak poses available.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Shoulder Mount (Wall Pedestal)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$700</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Wall pedestal shoulder mount with enhanced display base.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">European Mount (Boiled, Whitened & Hanger)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$100</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Cleaned, whitened, and sealed skull with antlers. Hanger included.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">European Mount (Natural)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$80</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Natural cleaned skull mount. A clean, classic look.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Velvet Preservation (Antlers)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$80</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Preserve velvet antlers in their natural state.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Predator Taxidermy -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 border-b-2 border-tan pb-2">
          Predator Taxidermy
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Predator Shoulder Mount</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$475</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Coyote, bobcat, fox, or other predator shoulder mount with lifelike detail.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Coyote (Life-Size)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$700–$1,000</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full life-size coyote mount. Price varies by pose and base complexity.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Bobcat (Life-Size)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$700–$1,000</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full life-size bobcat mount with natural positioning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Fox (Life-Size)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$700–$1,000</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full life-size fox mount. Red or gray fox.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Open Mouth Add-On (Predators)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$75–$150</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Add an open mouth or snarling expression to any predator mount.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Birds & Turkey -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 border-b-2 border-tan pb-2">
          Birds & Turkey
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Ducks (Flying)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$300</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Flying duck mount. Mallard, wood duck, teal, and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Ducks (Standing)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$275</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Standing or tabletop duck display on a natural base.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Turkey (Life-Size)</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$800</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full life-size turkey mount. Full strut, half strut, or flying poses.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Turkey Trophy Plaque</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$175</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Fan, beard, and spurs mounted on a custom plaque. A great way to display your gobbler.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Small Game -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 border-b-2 border-tan pb-2">
          Small Game
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Squirrel</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$180</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full body squirrel mount on a natural base. Novelty poses available.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Rabbit</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$275</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full body rabbit mount with natural positioning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Raccoon</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$300</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full body raccoon mount on a custom base.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Ground Hog</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$300</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Full body ground hog mount with natural positioning.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Services -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 border-b-2 border-tan pb-2">
          Additional Services
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Habitat / Base Work</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">$50–$300+</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Handcrafted driftwood, rock, and natural habitat bases to complement any mount.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal">Rush Orders</h3>
              <span class="text-tan-dark font-heading font-bold text-lg">+25%</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-earth text-sm">Need it sooner? Rush service available for an additional 25% on top of the standard price.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Turnaround & Notes -->
      <div class="bg-charcoal rounded-lg p-8 text-cream max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-tan mb-4 text-center">Good to Know</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tan mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-cream">Turnaround — European Mounts:</strong> 2–6 weeks.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tan mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-cream">Turnaround — Shoulder Mounts:</strong> 6–10 months.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tan mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-cream">Payment:</strong> 50% deposit at drop-off. Balance at pickup.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tan mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-cream">Field care required.</strong> Proper field care is essential before drop-off. See our <a href="/field-care" class="text-tan hover:text-tan-light underline">Field Care Guide</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tan mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-cream">Custom requests?</strong> We love unique projects. <a href="/contact" class="text-tan hover:text-tan-light underline">Contact us</a> to discuss.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
